            "CompanyDesc": "<p style=\"line-height: 13.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black;\"><strong>EduSmart</strong>&nbsp;represents a new way to nurture our next generations.&nbsp; At EduSmart, we make learning Chinese, English and Mathematics fun and memorable.&nbsp; We believe in &ldquo;<em><strong>Happy Children, Happy Results</strong></em>\" !&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 13.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black;\">EduSmart learning centres spreading across the territories: (HK Island): North Point, Mid-level; (Kowloon): Hung Hom, West Kowloon,</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black;\">Whampoa</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black;\">Lai Chi Kok &amp; Lam Tin; (NT): Ma On Shan, Fo Tan, Tseung Kwan O &amp; Yuen Long.&nbsp; EduSmart is part of Popular Holdings Ltd which also owns Popular Book Company, Educational Publishing House, Ltd. and Pan Lloyds Publishers.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 13.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black;\">If you are passionate about fun but effective learning and love to be around children, please join us!&nbsp; To cope with our rapid expansion, we are now inviting high caliber personnel to join our professional team.</span></p>",
            "JobDesc": "<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333; text-decoration: underline;\">Responsibilities:</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Managing the EduSmart Learning Centre for smooth operation;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Implement marketing activities, e.g. parents&rsquo; seminars and kids&rsquo; workshops;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Responsible for student recruitment;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Train tutors to conduct classes according to established learning methods and plans;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Establish and maintain the long-term customer relationship with parents;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Monitor the budget to ensure cost effectiveness and maintain the sustainable growth of student numbers;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Take up a relief tutorial role occasionally.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #333333; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Requirements:</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Degree holder, preferably in Education, Translation, Psychology or other related disciplines;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Minimum 3 years solid experience in teaching / learning centre management;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Familiar with the local kindergarten and primary education curriculum would be advantage;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Love children, be energetic, high initiative, self-motivated, independent and mature;</span></li>\n<li style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Immediate available</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Location: Lam Tin / Fo Tan / W9Z</span></strong></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333; text-decoration: underline;\">EduSmart offers</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><stro